      "observation": "step `upgrade_spring_boot_3_3` (jdk=17): BUILD FAILED post-recipe, rc=1\n--- first error cluster ---\n[22:05:12] PROJECT_ROOT=/work/src PHASE=build_post JDK=17\n[ERROR] COMPILATION ERROR : \n[ERROR] /work/src/src/main/java/com/mpalourdio/springboottemplate/model/entities/Task.java:[13,65] package org.hibernate.query.criteria.internal.expression.function does not exist\n[ERROR] /work/src/src/main/java/com/mpalourdio/springboottemplate/model/entities/Task.java:[45,20] cannot find symbol\n  symbol:   variable CurrentTimestampFunction\n  location: class com.mpalourdio.springboottemplate.model.entities.Task\n[ERROR] Failed to execute goal org.apache.maven.plugins:maven-compiler-plugin:3.13.0:compile (default-compile) on project springboottemplate: Compilation failure: Compilation failure: \n[ERROR] /work/src/src/main/java/com/mpalourdio/springboottemplate/model/entities/Task.java:[13,65] package org.hibernate.query.criteria.internal.expression.function does not exist\n[ERROR] /work/src/src/main/java/com/mpalourdio/springboottemplate/model/entities/Task.java:[45,20] cannot find symbol\n[ERROR]   symbol:   variable CurrentTimestampFunction\n[ERROR]   location: class com.mpalourdio.springboottemplate.model.entities.Task\n[ERROR] -> [Help 1]\n[ERROR] \n[ERROR] To see the full stack trace of the errors, re-run Maven with the -e switch.\n[ERROR] Re-run Maven using the -X switch to enable full debug logging.\n[ERROR] \n[ERROR] For more information about the errors and possible solutions, please read the following articles:\n[ERROR] [Help 1] http://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/MAVEN/MojoFailureException",
      "qwen_observation": "Hibernate 6 removed the internal class `CurrentTimestampFunction`, causing a compilation failure after the Spring Boot 3 upgrade step.",
      "qwen_rationale": "Inlining the `CurrentTimestampFunction.NAME` constant to its literal string value `\"current_timestamp\"` resolves the missing symbol error, as Hibernate 6's `@ColumnDefault` annotation still accepts the string. This fix is inserted immediately after the Spring Boot 3 upgrade step to patch the Hibernate 5 -> 6 migration gap."
    },
